#NJ #COVID19 #Vaccine New Demand Metric for NJ Counties

This looks at the DOD change of 1st and 2nd doses. In other words, how many 1st doses today from how many 1st doses yesterday, then ratios those.

Anything > 1.0 is more 1st than 2nd
Anything < 1.0 is more 2nd than 1st
